## ğŸ§Š Infrastructure Linked to JERT

Cryogas builds a network of **physical assets**, to which JERT is directly connected:

### 1. Cold Energy Terminals  
Using LNG cold energy for freezing, storage, fish processing, and B2B food-grade logistics.

### 2. LCNG Stations  
Full-cycle LNG import, storage, LNG-to-CNG production, high-pressure regasification.

### 3. B2B Logistics Hubs  
Container yards, reefer service zones, rail sidings, and multimodal consolidation nodes.

